This paper is about learning decentralized policies for cooperative multi-agent systems, which involves artificial intelligence (AI) and multi-agent systems (MA). Therefore, cs.AI and cs.MA are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also discusses the use of function approximation and distributed optimization, which are topics in machine learning (ML) and optimization (RO), respectively. Additionally, the paper deals with coordination and control in multi-agent systems, which are topics in systems and control (SY). Therefore, cs.LG, cs.RO, and cs.SY are also likely sub-categories.
